### Add checklist to all cards in the given column [PUT]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes (Checklist)

+ Response 201 (application/json)

## Data Structures

# Checklist

- name: Name of the new checklist (required, string)
- templateCard: `https://trello.com/cardId` (required, string)
- trelloToken: 5cd3f225d602413d8cb96ad7a9719137 (required, string)
- options (required, object)
    - One Of
        - card: `https://trello.com/c/cardId` (string)
        - Properties
            - board: `https://trello.com/b/boardId` (string)
            - column: name of column in Trello (string)